snippet.title: The Rewired Soul Speaks On Johnny Depp & Amber Heard Situation- My Reaction
snippet.description:
The Rewired Soul decided to jump on the Johnny Depp and Amber Heard bandwagon and share his experience. The Rewireed soul shares his past as a DV survisor. The Rewired Soul had great points but I do not agree with some. Here's my reaction and let me know if you agree with The Rewired soul! Thank you for watching and I'll see you in my next one!
xoxo- Kay
